you how to make these arrows,

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:41.680
so they are safe and they can't hit you,
even if they hit you in to face.

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:44.200
The goal is so that no matter how 
you shoot someone with these arrows,

00:05:44.200 --> 00:05:45.100
